      2. Verify installation by entering this command
    </div>
    <div class="step-code">
      <span style="color:rgb(40,160,160)">$</span> brew –v
    </div>
    <div class="step-title">
      3. You should see a result similar to this with a number for the x
    </div>
    <div class="step-code">
      Homebrew 0.9.x
    </div>
    <div class="step-title">
      4. To make sure homebrew is happy with your computer type
    </div>
    <div class="step-code">
      <span style="color:rgb(40,160,160)">$</span> brew doctor
    </div>
    <div class="step-title" style="padding-bottom:50px;">
